About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

Synopsis

‚ÄúThokai‚Äù is a dark comedy about Lila and Sampurai, two troublemakers who have failed Class VIII five times and are expelled for constantly cheating. Desperate for money, they see a job notice for a reporter and cameraman and start their own YouTube news channel. Instead of real journalism, they exploit poor people, pocketing donations meant for them, and thrive on spreading sensational and false stories.
Their greed turns dangerous when Lila tries to blackmail a student, threatening to post a fake video accusing him of using drugs. When the student can‚Äôt pay, Lila uploads the video, causing the boy to be disowned by his father, expelled from his hostel, and driven to suicide. Police soon crack down on Lila and Sampurai, exposing the cost of their fake news empire.

Zangeres - Swkang Debbarma, Permita Reang, Bishu Kr. Debbarma Subnur Tripura.

Samenvatting

"Thokai" is een zwarte komedie over Lila en Sampurai, twee onruststokers die vijf keer gezakt zijn voor klas 8 en van school gestuurd worden omdat ze constant spieken. Wanhopig op zoek naar geld zien ze een vacature voor een verslaggever en cameraman en beginnen ze hun eigen YouTube-nieuwskanaal. In plaats van echte journalistiek te bedrijven, buiten ze arme mensen uit, strijken ze donaties op die voor hen bestemd zijn en floreren ze met het verspreiden van sensationele en valse verhalen.
Hun hebzucht wordt gevaarlijk wanneer Lila een student probeert te chanteren en dreigt een nepvideo te plaatsen waarin hij van drugsgebruik wordt beschuldigd. Wanneer de student niet kan betalen, uploadt Lila de video, waardoor de jongen door zijn vader wordt verstoten, uit zijn studentenhuis wordt gezet en tot zelfmoord wordt gedreven. De politie treedt al snel hard op tegen Lila en Sampurai en onthult de prijs van hun nepnieuwsimperium.

Rumah Produksi - Shine Film Production.
Pemeran: Abir, Lila, Sulekha, Santa, Shankar Chimlang Uttam, Shymal Tarubala Bapan, Arjun Rabina, Jecob Bibash, Bishal Sujay, Himu, Biswanath Mokesh

Penyanyi: Swkang Debbarma, Permita Reang, Bishu Kr. Debbarma Subnur Tripura.

Sinopsis

"Thokai" adalah komedi gelap tentang Lila dan Sampurai, dua pembuat onar yang telah gagal di Kelas VIII sebanyak lima kali dan dikeluarkan karena terus-menerus menyontek. Karena sangat membutuhkan uang, mereka melihat lowongan pekerjaan untuk reporter dan juru kamera dan memulai kanal berita YouTube mereka sendiri. Alih-alih menjadi jurnalisme sejati, mereka mengeksploitasi orang miskin, mengantongi sumbangan yang seharusnya mereka terima, dan gemar menyebarkan berita sensasional dan palsu.
Keserakahan mereka berubah menjadi berbahaya ketika Lila mencoba memeras seorang siswa, mengancam akan mengunggah video palsu yang menuduhnya menggunakan narkoba. Ketika mahasiswa tersebut tidak mampu membayar, Lila mengunggah video tersebut, yang menyebabkan anak laki-laki itu diusir oleh ayahnya, dikeluarkan dari asrama, dan akhirnya bunuh diri. Polisi segera menindak Lila dan Sampurai, mengungkap kerugian yang ditimbulkan oleh kerajaan berita palsu mereka.

snippet.title: Sena - Guardians Of The Nation | Official Trailer | Amazon MX Player
snippet.description:
Amazon MX Player presents 
Sena - Guardians Of The Nation - Official Trailer 

Starring: @Funcho, @teekhabanao, Vikram Singh Chauhan, Yashpal Sharma, Shirley Setia, Neelu Dogra, Rahul Tewari, Vijay Vikram Singh, Anupam Bhattacharya, Anandeshwar Dwivedi
Special Appearances: Colonel Rajeev Bharwan, Lt Col Kaushalendra Singh, Lt Col Paishal Manocha, Colonel R. K. Sharma, Mr. Lucky Bisht.
Production House: 
Producers: Arunabh Kumar
Directors: Abhinav Anand
Writers: Anandeshwar Dwivedi
Genre: Drama, Suspense, Military & War

About Sena - Guardians Of The Nation: This story follows the bond between father Deen Dayal Sharma and son Kartik Sharma. Kartik leaves a good job in California to join the Indian Army, despite his father‚Äôs opposition. After clearing the CDS exam and SSB interview, he becomes a Captain posted in Kashmir. Their tense relationship and Kartik's SSB journey are shown in flashbacks. When militants attack and capture them, Kartik pretends to cooperate to plan an escape, sending a secret message to the Army. They flee through the jungle, and after a mishap, Kartik returns to India to lead a mission against the terrorist base.

About Amazon MX Player
Amazon MX Player is India‚Äôs leading free, premium, ad-supported entertainment service in India. It offers a diverse range of award-winning web series, reality shows, popular international shows, and a massive movie library across multiple genres. ‚ùØ‚ùØ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

Softwares used : Adobe Premiere Pro, After Effects & Photoshop.
Cutz & Design: Movie Cruzzer & team

snippet.title: Om Namo Bhagavate Vasudevaya Lyrical Video-Telugu | Mahavatar Narsimha | Hombale Films | Sam CS
snippet.description:
Om Namo Bhagavate Vasudevaya is a soulful Telugu devotional track sung by Vijay Prakash, with music by Sam CS. Featuring heartfelt lyrics by Saurabh Mittal, Twinkle Mittal, and Rakendu Mouli, the song is a prayerful ode to Lord Vishnu, expressing deep devotion, surrender, and spiritual longing.

Singer:  Vijay Prakash 
Lyricist: Saurabh Mittal, Twinkle Mittal, Rakendu Mouli
